*The last page of the diary*

23/08

That stubborn old fool Ulraunt. For years I had been tutored under him only to know his ignorance. He lectures me about ethics, yet it's a stubborn's fool way of granting true power. Power he wouldn't touch. Power he was too foolish to even fathom. 

Now I am right under his nose. I will show him true intellect, when I conquer candlekeep. Scholar's will know my vision. A vision of real knowledge and power.

Crudus Xentopia
